\[\|\bm{v}^{(k+1)}\|_{2}\leqslant\gamma^{k+1}\|\bm{v}^{(0)}\|_{2}+\alpha\|\bm{p} \|_{2}\sum_{j=0}^{k}\gamma^{j}=\gamma^{k+1}\|\bm{v}^{(0)}\|_{2}+\alpha\|\bm{p} \|_{2}\cdot\frac{1-\gamma^{k+1}}{1-\gamma},\]

for all \(k\in\mathbb{N}\). Therefore, \(\{\bm{v}^{(k)}\}_{k\in\mathbb{N}}\) is bounded, since \(\gamma\in(0,1)\). 

